<topic id="how-to-oracle11g">
  <title>How to Oracle 11g Support</title>
  <body>
    <p>Follow this procedure to configure the support for a Oracle 11g database:<ol>
        <li><ph
            conref="download-database-drivers.dita#download-database-drivers/download_oracle_driver"
          /></li>
        <li><xref href="../tasks/configure-oracle-datasource.dita#configure-oracle-datasource"
            >Configure a Oracle 11g <term>Data Source</term> driver.</xref></li>
        <li><xref href="../tasks/configure-oracle-connection.dita#configure-oracle-connection"
            >Configure a Oracle 11g <term>Connection</term>.</xref></li>
        <li>Use the <uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol> view from the <menucascade>
            <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol>Show View</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol>
          </menucascade> menu or switch to the <uicontrol>Database Perspective</uicontrol>
          (available from <menucascade>
            <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol>Open Perspective</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol>Database</uicontrol>
          </menucascade>).</li>
      </ol></p>
